-------
vim configuration [through edit ~/.vimrc]
-------
1. let vi show/hide line number?
set number 
set nonumber

2. let tab occupy 4 spaces?
set tabstop=4

3. let tab be auto replaced with 4 spaces?
set expandtab

-------
vim usage
-------
1. jump to inner block pair and func block pair?
inner block pair: [{ ]}
function block pair: [[ ]]
ref: http://vim.wikia.com/wiki/Jumping_to_the_start_and_end_of_a_code_block
